Subject: Sharepoint Scan not working after update of NEA incl. Proxies and Agents
Description: After updating NEA to the current version, the sharepoint jobs are not scanning anymore. The agents were updated on the servers and the proxies also. Error message: Agent Service WSB-GROUPSHARE.RKW.INT already executing scan for host WSB-GROUPSHARE.RKW.INT PrepareTask for DC 'SHAREPOINTACCESS' for task 'SharePoint Scan' failed: Unspecified error
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Run a SPAA scan to get an error after an upgrade
